HOW TO RUN



Create a design file, for the fulladder4 as given in the repository
Create a design file for the adders that fulladder4 calls as given in the repository
just create one
Create a simulation file (testbench) and copy the code in there
Run simulation and verify if everything and all the outputs are fine
After that run synthesis
Add a constraint file and add the code as given
run synthesis
run implementation
run bitstream
click on program device and it shall work

NOTE THAT UR DEVICE MUST BE CONNECETED TO YOUR LAPTOP AND IS DETECTED.


THE SUM WILL BE SHOWN ON THE LEDS 0-4 use the switches to change the numbers
